"If special character (e.g. umlauts) do not show up correctly, the data file "
"probably uses a different locale than your R session. In this case, check "
"this option, and specify the correct character encoding below."
msgstr ""
"Mura bhfuil carachtair speisialta (m.sh. umlauts) le feiceáil i gceart, is "
"dócha go n-úsáideann an comhad sonraí logán difriúil ná do sheisiún R. Sa "
"chás seo, seiceáil an rogha seo, agus sonraigh an ionchódú carachtar ceart "
"thíos."

