msgstr ""
"Leibhéal comhbhrúite. Léiríonn luachanna níos airde comhbhrú níos fearr."

#. i18n: ectx: (Loaded from Save R objects) <settings> <setting> (refers to element labelled "Enable xz extreme compression")
